{"can_edit": true, "from": {"id": "1312089751", "name": "Peter Boyd"}, "revision": "10151881980795019", "updated_time": "2012-06-20T19:29:56+0000", "can_delete": true, "created_time": "2012-06-20T19:29:56+0000", "message": "<p>A lot of people here ask questions about different aspects of Linux.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Since answering these questions again and again is a tedious work, i  will try to summarize some of the important topics that may be of  interest to new Linux users...</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>First of all if you decided to test Linux, choose you distro and  download/burn its LiveCD version (if such version is offered). That will  help you in your decision.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Choosing the right distro is usually hard, because you get quite a bunch of opinions which distro is better, which sucks etc...</p>\n<p>But these links may help you choose:</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Distrowatch -&gt; <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdistrowatch.com%2Fdwres.php%3Fresource%3Dmajor&amp;h=-AQFn4SB_&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/distrowatch.com\\/dwres.php?resource=major&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fdistrowatch.com\\u00252Fdwres.php\\u00253Fresource\\u00253Dmajor&amp;h=-AQFn4SB_&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://distrowatch.com/dwres.php?resource=major</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Linux Wizard -&gt; <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zegeniestudios.net%2Fldc%2Findex.php%3Fselect_lang%3Dtrue&amp;h=dAQEZJGRF&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.zegeniestudios.net\\/ldc\\/index.php?select_lang=true&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.zegeniestudios.net\\u00252Fldc\\u00252Findex.php\\u00253Fselect_lang\\u00253Dtrue&amp;h=dAQEZJGRF&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.zegeniestudios.net/ldc/index.php?select_lang=true</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>After you install your distribution and get a bit acquainted with it you may like to have a look at some of the following:</p>\n<p>==============================================================</p>\n<ol><li>Make sure you only add to your repositories <strong>trusted sources</strong> </li>\n<li>Make sure you have activated <strong>all your distro&#039;s security updates</strong> and general updates repositories</li>\n<li>You may add some additional repositories that offer new versions of some packages like KDE, some multimedia programs etc</li>\n</ol><p>\u00a0</p>\n<ul><li><strong>Ubuntu family</strong>:</li>\n</ul><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Backports - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaunchpad.net%2F%7Ekubuntu-ppa&amp;h=yAQElDa1R&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/launchpad.net\\/~kubuntu-ppa&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=https\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Flaunchpad.net\\u00252F\\u00257Ekubuntu-ppa&amp;h=yAQElDa1R&amp;s=1&quot;);\">https://launchpad.net/~kubuntu-ppa</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.ubuntu.com%2Fcommunity%2FRepositories%2FKubuntu&amp;h=LAQHf9ECj&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/help.ubuntu.com\\/community\\/Repositories\\/Kubuntu&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=https\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fhelp.ubuntu.com\\u00252Fcommunity\\u00252FRepositories\\u00252FKubuntu&amp;h=LAQHf9ECj&amp;s=1&quot;);\">https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Repositories/Kubuntu</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Medibuntu - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedibuntu.org%2Frepository.php&amp;h=PAQGI3B6m&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/medibuntu.org\\/repository.php&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fmedibuntu.org\\u00252Frepository.php&amp;h=PAQGI3B6m&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://medibuntu.org/repository.php</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Wine - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winehq.org%2Fdownload%2Fubuntu&amp;h=5AQGxDvCt&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.winehq.org\\/download\\/ubuntu&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.winehq.org\\u00252Fdownload\\u00252Fubuntu&amp;h=5AQGxDvCt&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.winehq.org/download/ubuntu</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 VirtualBox - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.virtualbox.org%2Fwiki%2FLinux_Downloads&amp;h=PAQGI3B6m&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/www.virtualbox.org\\/wiki\\/Linux_Downloads&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=https\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.virtualbox.org\\u00252Fwiki\\u00252FLinux_Downloads&amp;h=PAQGI3B6m&amp;s=1&quot;);\">https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Linux_Downloads</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<ul><li><strong>Mandriva</strong>: </li>\n</ul><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 The PLF Repos - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Feasyurpmi.zarb.org%2F&amp;h=oAQFVyR-J&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/easyurpmi.zarb.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Feasyurpmi.zarb.org\\u00252F&amp;h=oAQFVyR-J&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://easyurpmi.zarb.org/</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<ul><li><strong>Fedora</strong>:</li>\n</ul><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Read this first -\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffedoraproject.org%2Fwiki%2FThird_party_repositories&amp;h=fAQE3I-W6&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/fedoraproject.org\\/wiki\\/Third_party_repositories&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Ffedoraproject.org\\u00252Fwiki\\u00252FThird_party_repositories&amp;h=fAQE3I-W6&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Third_party_repositories</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 RPM Fusion - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Frpmfusion.org%2FConfiguration&amp;h=ZAQHq9mnm&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/rpmfusion.org\\/Configuration&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Frpmfusion.org\\u00252FConfiguration&amp;h=ZAQHq9mnm&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://rpmfusion.org/Configuration</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Linva (Add RPM Fusion FIRST) -\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Frpm.livna.org%2F&amp;h=xAQFXRFcG&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/rpm.livna.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Frpm.livna.org\\u00252F&amp;h=xAQFXRFcG&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://rpm.livna.org/</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<ul><li><strong>openSuse</strong>:</li>\n</ul><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Read this first -\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.opensuse.org%2FPackage_repositories&amp;h=JAQHrv6cB&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/en.opensuse.org\\/Package_repositories&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fen.opensuse.org\\u00252FPackage_repositories&amp;h=JAQHrv6cB&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://en.opensuse.org/Package_repositories</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Packman - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.opensuse.org%2FAdditional_package_repositories&amp;h=rAQEGLwxq&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/en.opensuse.org\\/Additional_package_repositories&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fen.opensuse.org\\u00252FAdditional_package_repositories&amp;h=rAQEGLwxq&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://en.opensuse.org/Additional_package_repositories</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Note that most repos in SuSE are available under &quot;add repository&quot; and selecting &quot;Community Repository&quot;.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<ul><li>Pardus:</li>\n</ul><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Read this first for installation and more: <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.pardus-wiki.org%2FInstallation%3AContents&amp;h=eAQF1oy3s&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/en.pardus-wiki.org\\/Installation:Contents&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fen.pardus-wiki.org\\u00252FInstallation\\u00253AContents&amp;h=eAQF1oy3s&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://en.pardus-wiki.org/Installation:Contents</a></p>\n<p>PardusRepo - <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fworldforum.pardus-linux.nl%2Findex.php%3Ftopic%3D3478.0&amp;h=9AQEwxq-D&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/worldforum.pardus-linux.nl\\/index.php?topic=3478.0&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fworldforum.pardus-linux.nl\\u00252Findex.php\\u00253Ftopic\\u00253D3478.0&amp;h=9AQEwxq-D&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://worldforum.pardus-linux.nl/index.php?topic=3478.0</a> (Second post from Atobloo).</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Some security related remarks:</p>\n<p>====================</p>\n<ol><li>Avoid installing unnecessary services. Like if you do not intend  accessing your computer remotely, do not install the SSH server etc</li>\n<li><strong>Never give your root password (or root access) to anyone</strong> you do not entirely trust</li>\n<li><strong>Do not run scripts from unknown sources</strong> especially do not run them  as root. Same goes for installing packages from untrusted sources... </li>\n</ol><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Finally if you feel lost among the pile of applications that Linux offers you, and you need some help in finding alternatives/analogues of  you favorite MS Windows programs.... You may consult the Linux  Alternative Project (formerly the Linux Equivalent Project) -&gt; <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxalt.com%2F&amp;h=IAQFH24Ti&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.linuxalt.com\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.linuxalt.com\\u00252F&amp;h=IAQFH24Ti&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.linuxalt.com/</a></p>", "subject": "Linux First Steps and \"Rules\"", "id": "10151881980825019", "icon": "https://fbstatic-a.akamaihd.net/rsrc.php/v2/y7/r/8zhNI-VGpiI.png"}